      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mb-6">A three-phase decanter centrifuge separates solids plus two immiscible liquids — such as oil, water, and solids — in a single pass. Where two separate machines would otherwise be required, the three-phase decanter accomplishes the same result in one compact, continuous process.</p>
